tions.png" data-adults-dark="../assets/a1-08-adults-dark-scene-04-instructions.png" src="../assets/a1-08-kids-light-scene-04-instructions.png" alt="Instructions review scene"><span>Instructions</span></figure></div><div class="prompt-grid"><div class="prompt-card"><label><input type="checkbox" data-obs> <span data-kids="Alex wakes up and gets ready for school." data-adults="Mia starts work at her desk in the morning.">Alex wakes up and gets ready for school.</span></label></div><div class="prompt-card"><label><input type="checkbox" data-obs> <span data-kids="Alex has a school bag and two notebooks." data-adults="Mia has a laptop, a phone, and documents.">Alex has a school bag and two notebooks.</span></label></div><div class="prompt-card"><label><input type="checkbox" data-obs> <span data-kids="His bag is under the desk." data-adults="Her phone is next to the coffee mug.">His bag is under the desk.</span></label></div><div class="prompt-card"><label><input type="checkbox" data-obs> <span data-kids="Mia says: Put the pencils in the cup." data-adults="Alex says: Can you move the documents, please?">Mia says: Put the pencils in the cup.</span></label></div><div class="prompt-card"><label><input type="checkbox" data-obs> <span>There is a desk in the room.</span></label></div><div class="prompt-card"><label><input type="checkbox" data-obs> <span>There are books on the desk.</span></label></div><div class="prompt-card"><label><input type="checkbox" data-obs> <span data-kids="The football is next to the chair." data-adults="The keys are in front of the work bag.">The football is next to the chair.</span></label></div><div class="prompt-card"><label><input type="checkbox" data-obs> <span data-kids="Put them in the cup." data-adults="Put them between the laptop and the lamp.">Put them in the cup.</span></label></div></div><div class="block-nav"><a class="btn primary" href="#grammar-review">Next: grammar review</a></div></section>

  <section class="block" id="grammar-review"><header class="block-head"><div class="block-num">04</div><div class="block-title-wrap"><div class="block-kicker">Grammar Review</div><h2 class="block-title">Your A1 grammar table</h2></div><div class="block-time">≈ 8 min</div></header><div class="grammar-table-wrap"><table class="grammar-table"><thead><tr><th>Topic</th><th>Formula</th><th>Example</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Present Simple</td><td class="formula">subject + verb</td><td class="sample">I wake up at seven. She works at home.</td></tr><tr><td>Questions</td><td class="formula">Do / Does + subject + base verb?</td><td class="sample">Do you have a notebook? Does Alex wake up early?</td></tr><tr><td>Negatives</td><td class="formula">don't / doesn't + base verb</td><td class="sample">I don't have a TV. Mia doesn't have a printer.</td></tr><tr><td>There is / There are</td><td class="formula">there is + one / there are + many</td><td class="sample">There is a desk. There are two books.</td></tr><tr><td>Have / Has</td><td class="formula">I/you/we/they have · he/she/it has</td><td class="sample">Alex has a bag. We have pencils.</td></tr><tr><td>Possessives</td><td class="formula">my / your / his / her / our / their + noun</td><td class="sample">It is his bag. These are their keys.</td></tr><tr><td>Prepositions</td><td class="formula">in / on / under / next to / between / behind / in front of</td><td class="sample">The bag is under the desk. The phone is next to the mug.</td></tr><tr><td>Instructions</td><td class="formula">put / move + object + place</td><td class="sample">Put it on the desk. Move them next to the laptop.</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="grammar-rule"><strong>Final rule:</strong> Keep A1 sentences simple. Use one clear idea in one sentence: person + action + object + place.</div><div class="error-card"><h3>Final mistake check</h3><p><span class="bad">Wrong:</span> Does Alex has a bag? / This is I notebook. / Put them on desk.<br><span class="good">Right:</span> Does Alex have a bag? / This is my notebook. / Put them on the desk.</p></div><div class="block-nav"><a class="btn primary" href="#mini-mission">Next: mini mission</a></div></section>

  <section class="block" id="mini-mission"><header class="block-head"><div class="block-num">05</div><div class="block-title-wrap"><div class="block-kicker">Mini Mission</div><h2 class="block-title">Build a final story</h2></div><div class="block-time">≈ 9 min</div></header><p class="block-intro">Click the sentence cards in the correct order. This is a small final story that connects all grammar blocks.</p><div class="mission-board"><div class="story-builder"><div class="story-bank"><h3>Sentence bank</h3><div class="bank" id="storyBank"></div></div><div class="story-output"><h3>Your story</h3><ol id="storyOutput"></ol></div></div><div class="story-actions"><button class="btn primary" id="checkStoryBtn">Check story</button><button class="btn ghost" id="resetStoryBtn">Reset</button><span class="story-score" id="storyScore">Score: 0 / 8</span></div></div><div class="block-nav"><a class="btn primary" href="#mixed-practice">Next: mixed practice</a></div></section>

