  <section class="block" id="final-project"><header class="block-head"><div class="block-num">07</div><div class="block-title-wrap"><div class="block-kicker">Final Project</div><h2 class="block-title">Write or record your A1 story</h2></div><div class="block-time">≈ 15 min</div></header><p class="block-intro">Write or record 8–10 sentences about your day, your room or workspace, your things, where they are, and simple instructions. Add 2 questions and 2 instructions.</p><div class="recorder"><strong>Optional recorder</strong><p class="minitask-detail">Record your final story and play it back.</p><div class="recorder-controls"><span class="record-dot" data-record-dot></span><button class="btn primary" data-record-start>Start recording</button><button class="btn ghost" data-record-stop disabled>Stop</button><audio controls data-record-audio></audio></div></div><textarea class="write-box" data-final-draft data-kids="Write 8–10 sentences:&#10;I wake up at seven.&#10;I have a school bag.&#10;This is my notebook.&#10;There is a desk in my room.&#10;My football is next to the chair.&#10;Put the pencils in the cup.&#10;Can you put it on the desk?" data-adults="Write 8–10 sentences:&#10;I work at my desk.&#10;I have a laptop.&#10;This is my coffee mug.&#10;There is a lamp on the desk.&#10;My phone is next to the laptop.&#10;Put the documents between the laptop and the lamp.&#10;Can you move them, please?" placeholder="Write 8–10 sentences..."></textarea><div class="check-grid" style="margin-top:14px"><article class="info-card"><h3>Project checklist</h3><div class="now-grid"><div class="now-item"><label><input type="checkbox" data-final> I wrote 8–10 sentences.</label></div><div class="now-item"><label><input type="checkbox" data-final> I used a routine sentence.</label></div><div class="now-item"><label><input type="checkbox" data-final> I used have / has.</label></div><div class="now-item"><label><input type="checkbox" data-final> I used my / your / his / her.</label></div><div class="now-item"><label><input type="checkbox" data-final> I used there is / there are.</label></div><div class="now-item"><label><input type="checkbox" data-final> I used prepositions.</label></div><div class="now-item"><label><input type="checkbox" data-final> I wrote 2 questions.</label></div><div class="now-item"><label><input type="checkbox" data-final> I wrote 2 instructions.</label></div></div></article><article class="info-card"><h3>Certificate condition</h3><p>Your project must be submitted before the certificate unlocks. Use the checklist and write at least 45 words.</p></article><article class="info-card"><h3>Then test</h3><p>After the project, complete all 8 test rounds. You need at least 45 / 64 to pass.</p></article></div><div class="block-nav"><a class="btn primary" href="#bonus-test">Next: bonus test</a></div></section>

  <section class="block" id="bonus-test"><header class="block-head"><div class="block-num">08</div><div class="block-title-wrap"><div class="block-kicker">Final Interactive Test</div><h2 class="block-title">8 rounds × 8 tasks = 64 tasks</h2></div><div class="block-time">≈ 30–45 min</div></header><p class="block-intro">This is the big final A1 checkpoint. It includes choices, sentence building, fixing mistakes, matching, visual checks, mini-dialogues, and short answers.</p><div class="test-summary"><div class="summary-card"><strong id="testScoreBig">0 / 64</strong><small>Final test score</small></div><div class="summary-card"><strong id="testProgressBig">0 / 64</strong><small>Tasks completed</small></div><div class="summary-card"><strong id="testStatusBig">Locked</strong><small>Certificate status</small></div></div><div class="test-shell"><div class="round-list" id="roundList"></div><div class="round-panel"><div class="round-head"><div class="round-title-line"><div><span class="round-stats" id="roundKicker">Round 1 / 8</span><h3 id="roundTitle">Present Simple routines</h3></div><span class="round-stats" id="roundScore">0 / 8</span></div><div class="round-track"><span class="round-fill" id="roundFill"></span></div><div class="round-stats" id="roundNote">Complete all tasks in this round.</div></div><div class="task-list" id="taskList"></div><div class="block-nav" style="padding:0 18px 18px"><button class="btn ghost" id="prevRoundBtn">Previous round</button><button class="btn primary" id="nextRoundBtn">Next round</button></div></div></div><div class="block-nav"><a class="btn primary" href="#certificate-unlock">Next: certificate unlock</a></div></section>

