  <section class="block" id="certificate"><header class="block-head"><div class="block-num">10</div><div class="block-title-wrap"><div class="block-kicker">Electronic Certificate</div><h2 class="block-title">Certificate of Completion</h2></div><div class="block-time">≈ 3 min</div></header><div class="certificate-shell"><div class="certificate" id="certificatePrint"><div class="cert-content"><div class="cert-logo"><span>Lingua</span><span>Boost</span><span style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:14px;color:var(--accent);border:2px solid var(--accent);padding:3px 6px;border-radius:6px;letter-spacing:.08em">LAB</span></div><div class="cert-kicker" id="certAudienceTitle">A1 English Explorer Certificate</div><h2 class="cert-title">Certificate of Completion</h2><p style="font-size:18px;color:var(--muted)">This certifies that</p><div class="cert-name" id="certName">Student Name</div><p style="font-size:18px;color:var(--muted)">has successfully completed</p><div class="cert-course">LinguaBoost Lab · A1 Mini-Course</div><div class="cert-seal">★</div><div class="cert-meta-grid"><div class="cert-meta"><small>Final Score</small><strong id="certScore">0 / 64</strong></div><div class="cert-meta"><small>Level</small><strong>A1 Foundation</strong></div><div class="cert-meta"><small>Date</small><strong id="certDate">—</strong></div><div class="cert-meta"><small>Certificate ID</small><strong id="certId">—</strong></div></div><p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:760px;line-height:1.65">The learner completed the final project and passed the interactive A1 checkpoint covering routines, questions, negatives, there is / there are, have / has, possessives, prepositions, and instructions.</p></div></div></div></section>

